Class DaoJpaHibernate

java.lang.Object
openDao.operation.DaoJpaHibernate

public class DaoJpaHibernate extends Object implements DaoOperationFacade, Serializable
DaoJpaHibernate implement the interface DaoOperationFacade Implement the operations of database for framework JPA - Hibernate All classes that need to work with database
